"overall_meaning": "Then Indra, reaching the gods, saw this fear:  Just as this body, when beautified, becomes beautified, fragrant, and purified, so too, in this blindness, one becomes blind, weak, and decayed.  This body seeks destruction, it perishes.  Here I do not see enjoyment."
